WEBVTT

00:00:11.657 --> 00:00:17.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Can you see
with your mind’s eye,

00:00:17.204 --> 00:00:22.668 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Peoples
dwelling together?

00:00:22.668 --> 00:00:28.257 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sorrow has passed.
Peace at last!

00:00:28.257 --> 00:00:33.345 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Life without
tears or pain.

00:00:33.345 --> 00:00:39.184 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sing out
with joy of heart!

00:00:39.184 --> 00:00:44.732 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You too
can have a part.

00:00:44.732 --> 00:00:50.195 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Live for the day
when you’ll say,

00:00:50.195 --> 00:00:56.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‏“Life without end,
at last!”

00:01:04.168 --> 00:01:09.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In those days
old will grow young,

00:01:09.381 --> 00:01:14.762 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Flesh revived
as in childhood.

00:01:14.762 --> 00:01:20.351 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Troubles are gone,
from now on,

00:01:20.351 --> 00:01:25.814 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No need
to weep or fear.

00:01:25.814 --> 00:01:31.445 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sing out
with joy of heart!

00:01:31.445 --> 00:01:36.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You too
can have a part.

00:01:36.825 --> 00:01:42.498 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Live for the day
when you’ll say,

00:01:42.498 --> 00:01:48.504 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Life without end,
at last!”

00:01:56.011 --> 00:02:01.517 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Paradise
all will enjoy

00:02:01.517 --> 00:02:07.106 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As we sing
of God’s glory.

00:02:07.106 --> 00:02:12.528 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Long as we live,
we will give

00:02:12.528 --> 00:02:17.658 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To God, our Maker,
thanks.

00:02:17.658 --> 00:02:23.455 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sing out
with joy of heart!

00:02:23.455 --> 00:02:29.003 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You too
can have a part.

00:02:29.003 --> 00:02:34.508 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Live for the day
when you’ll say,

